ttp_template:
<group name="enabled_link_status_log_index_log_interface">
Physical interface: ge-0/0/0, {{ENABLED | ORPHRASE}}, Physical link is Up
Physical interface: {{PHYS_INTERFACE}}, Enabled, Physical link is {{LINK_STATUS | ORPHRASE}}
  Logical interface {{LOG_INTERFACE}} (Index {{LOG_INDEX}}) (SNMP ifIndex {{SNMP_IF_INDEX | ORPHRASE}})
  Output bytes  : {{OUTPUT_BYTES | ORPHRASE}}
  Output packets: {{OUTPUT_PACKETS | ORPHRASE}}
</group>
cli_content:
Physical interface: ge-0/0/0, Enabled, Physical link is Up
    Logical interface ge-0/0/0.0 (Index 333) (SNMP ifIndex 710)
    Flags: Up SNMP-Traps 0x4004000 Encapsulation: ENET2
    Traffic statistics:

textfsm_template:
Value PHYS_INTERFACE (\S+)
Value ENABLED (\S+)
Value LINK_STATUS (\S+)
Value LOG_INTERFACE (\S+)
Value LOG_INDEX (\d+)
Value SNMP_IF_INDEX (\d+)
Value FLAGS (\S+)
Value ENCAPSULATION (\S+)
Value INPUT_BYTES (\d+)
Value OUTPUT_BYTES (\d+)
Value INPUT_PACKETS (\d+)
Value OUTPUT_PACKETS (\d+)

Start
  ^Physical\sinterface:\s${PHYS_INTERFACE},\s${ENABLED},\sPhysical\slink\sis\s${LINK_STATUS}
  ^\s*Logical\sinterface\s${LOG_INTERFACE}\s\(Index\s${LOG_INDEX}\)\s\(SNMP\sifIndex\s${SNMP_IF_INDEX}\)
  ^\s*Flags:\s${FLAGS}\sEncapsulation:\s${ENCAPSULATION}
  ^\s*Traffic\sstatistics:
  ^\s*Input\sbytes\s*:\s${INPUT_BYTES}
  ^\s*Output\sbytes\s*:\s${OUTPUT_BYTES}
  ^\s*Input\spackets\s*:\s${INPUT_PACKETS}
  ^\s*Output\spackets\s*:\s${OUTPUT_PACKETS}
